<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM7.3.8">
<l>iṉiyeppā vamvantey tuñcollī remakkimmai yēyaruḷ peṟṟamai yālaṭum</l>
<l>tuṉiyaittīrt tiṉpamētaru kiṉṟatōrtōṟ ṟattoṉ ṉeṟiyai vaiyan toḻappaṭum</l>
<l>muṉiyai vāṉava rālvaṇaṅ kappaṭum muttiṉaip pattartām nukarkiṉṟatōr</l>
<l>kaṉiyai kātalcey teṉṉuḷḷaṅ koṇṭakaḷva ṉaiyiṉṟu kaṇṭukoṇ ṭēṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Tell [us] what misfortune would come and befall us hereafter</l>
<l rend="indent">with the receipt of grace in this life;</l>
<l>I saw for myself today the ancient bright path which is the giving of delight,</l>
<l rend="indent">ending sorrows which torment,</l>
<l>The sage who is worshipped by the world, the pearl revered by the celestials,</l>
<l>The fruit which is the enjoyment of bhaktas, the thief who stole my heart, inciting love.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
